{
  "id": "service_contract",
  "name": "服务合同模板",
  "category": "contract",
  "version": "1.0",
  "description": "完整服务合同模板，包含甲乙方信息、服务条款、付款方式、违约责任、签章区",
  "variables": {
    "required": [
      "counterparty",
      "service_content",
      "amount",
      "start_date",
      "end_date"
    ],
    "optional": [
      "payment_terms",
      "penalty_clause",
      "special_terms"
    ]
  },
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "title",
      "heading": "服务合同",
      "level": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "metadata",
      "content": {
        "contract_number": "{{auto_generate:HT-YYYYMM-XXX}}",
        "signing_date": "{{auto_date:YYYY-MM-DD}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "甲方（委托方）",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "- **名称**: {{counterparty}}\n- **地址**: {{counterparty_address|optional}}\n- **联系人**: {{counterparty_contact|optional}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "乙方（服务方）",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "- **名称**: {{company.name}}\n- **联系人**: {{company.owner_name}}\n- **联系方式**: {{company.owner_contact}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第一条 服务内容",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "{{service_content}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第二条 合同期限",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "自 **{{start_date}}** 起至 **{{end_date}}** 止。"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第三条 合同金额及付款方式",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "合同总金额：**人民币 {{amount|format:currency}} 元整**。\n\n{{payment_terms|default:合同签订后 30 日内，甲方向乙方支付合同全额。}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第四条 双方权利义务",
      "level": 2,
      "subsections": [
        {
          "heading": "甲方权利义务",
          "level": 3,
          "content": "1. 按时支付合同款项；\n2. 配合乙方提供必要的资料和工作条件；\n3. 有权对服务质量进行监督和验收。"
        },
        {
          "heading": "乙方权利义务",
          "level": 3,
          "content": "1. 按照合同约定提供专业服务；\n2. 保守甲方商业秘密和技术秘密；\n3. 按期完成服务交付。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第五条 违约责任",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "{{penalty_clause|default:任何一方违反本合同约定的，应向守约方支付合同总金额 10% 的违约金。}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第六条 争议解决",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "本合同在履行过程中如发生争议，双方应友好协商解决；协商不成的，任何一方均可向乙方所在地人民法院提起诉讼。"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "第七条 其他",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "1. 本合同一式两份，甲乙双方各持一份，具有同等法律效力。\n2. 本合同未尽事宜，由双方另行协商补充。\n\n{{special_terms|optional}}"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "signature_block",
      "content": "**甲方（盖章）**：________________　　**乙方（盖章）**：________________\n\n**授权代表**：________________　　　　**授权代表**：________________\n\n**日期**：________________　　　　　　**日期**：________________"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "author": "星环OPC团队",
    "created_at": "2026-02-28",
    "updated_at": "2026-02-28",
    "tags": ["合同", "服务", "标准模板"],
    "language": "zh-CN",
    "applicable_regions": ["中国大陆"]
  },
  "validation_rules": [
    {
      "field": "amount",
      "rule": "must_be_positive",
      "message": "合同金额必须大于 0"
    },
    {
      "field": "end_date",
      "rule": "must_be_after",
      "compare_to": "start_date",
      "message": "结束日期必须晚于开始日期"
    }
  ],
  "export_options": {
    "formats": ["docx", "pdf"],
    "default_format": "docx",
    "page_size": "A4",
    "margins": {
      "top": 2.5,
      "right": 2,
      "bottom": 2.5,
      "left": 2,
      "unit": "cm"
    },
    "font": {
      "family": "宋体",
      "size": 12,
      "line_height": 1.5
    }
  }
}
